'''同性婚姻'''在[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]经过新墨西哥州最高法院在年12月19日的裁决成为全州法律。在此之前，[[新墨西哥州行政区划|33个县]]中共有8个可以或计划为同性伴侣颁发结婚证。这8个县覆盖全州58％的人口。新墨西哥州法律并没有明确允许或禁止同性婚姻，它是唯一缺乏州法规或宪法规定来明确解决同性婚姻问题的州份。<ref name=stateline>{{cite news|last=Grovum|first=Jake|title=How New Mexico Legalized Gay Marriage – For 8 Hours|url=http://www.pewstates.org/projects/stateline/headlines/how-new-mexico-legalized-gay-marriage-for-8-hours-85899450437|accessdate=2013-05-09|newspaper=Stateline|date=2013-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140412171303/http://www.pewstates.org/projects/stateline/headlines/how-new-mexico-legalized-gay-marriage-for-8-hours-85899450437|archive-date=2014-04-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

[[桑多瓦爾縣|桑多瓦爾縣]]在2004年曾经允许一小部分同性伴侣登记结婚。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.abqjournal.com/news/state/apwed02-20-04.htm|title=Same-Sex Couples Line Up in Sandoval County To Get Married|date=2004-02-20|accessdate=2013-08-27|agency=Albuquerque Journal|archive-date=2021-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210202627/https://www.abqjournal.com/news/state/apwed02-20-04.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>这种做法在同一天新墨西哥州总检察长提起诉讼后被叫停。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://lubbockonline.com/stories/022105/reg_022105070.shtml|agency=Lubbock Online|title=Ex-Sandoval clerk writing book on same-sex marriage|date=2005-02-21|accessdate=2013-08-27|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006132855/http://lubbockonline.com/stories/022105/reg_022105070.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年8月21日，[[唐娜安娜縣|唐娜安娜縣]]的工作人员开始主动给同性伴侣颁发结婚证书。此后，三个地区法官先后裁决同性伴侣可以登记结婚，依次是[[圣菲县|圣菲县]]，[[伯納利歐縣|伯納利歐縣]]和[[陶斯縣_(新墨西哥州)|陶斯縣]]，<ref name=huff>{{cite news|last=Clausing|first=Jeri|title=New Mexico Judge Declares Same-Sex Marriage Legal|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/08/26/new-mexico-same-sex-marriage_n_3817458.html|accessdate=2013-08-29|newspaper=Huffington Post|date=2013-08-26|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310070215/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/08/26/new-mexico-same-sex-marriage_n_3817458.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.taosnews.com/news/article_161e50d2-0f6e-11e3-8da6-001a4bcf887a.html|agency=The Taos News|title=Same-sex couples to wed in Taos County|date=2013-08-27|accessdate=2013-08-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130901222420/http://www.taosnews.com/news/article_161e50d2-0f6e-11e3-8da6-001a4bcf887a.html|archivedate=2013年9月1日}}</ref>9月，第四个法官同样裁决[[格蘭特縣_(新墨西哥州)|格蘭特縣]]也可登记。<ref name="grant">{{cite news|url=http://www.abqjournal.com/257162/abqnewsseeker/los-alamos-county-faces-gay-marriage-decision.html|agency=Albuquerque Journal|title=7th New Mexico county plans to allow gay marriage|date=2013-09-03|accessdate=2013-09-03|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422073034/http://www.abqjournal.com/257162/abqnewsseeker/los-alamos-county-faces-gay-marriage-decision.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[洛斯阿拉莫斯縣|洛斯阿拉莫斯縣]]作出类似裁决，但被质疑。9月4日维持原判后开始颁发结婚证书。<ref name="la">{{cite news|url=http://www.abqjournal.com/255303/politics/los-alamos-county-on-verge-of-becoming-seventh-nm-county-to-issue-same-sex-marriage-licenses.html|agency=Albuquerque Journal|title=Los Alamos County on verge of becoming seventh NM county to issue same-sex marriage licenses|date=2013-08-29|accessdate=2013-08-29|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212505/http://www.abqjournal.com/255303/politics/los-alamos-county-on-verge-of-becoming-seventh-nm-county-to-issue-same-sex-marriage-licenses.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="krqe">{{cite news|url=http://www.krqe.com/news/local/clerk-say-she-wont-issue-licenses-yet?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=twitter|agency=KRQE|title=Clerk say she won't issue licenses yet|date=2013-09-03|accessdate=2013-09-03}}</ref><ref name="kob">{{cite news|url=http://www.kob.com/article/stories/S3148764.shtml?cat=500|agency=KOB|title=Judge upholds ruling for Los Alamos County clerk to issue same-sex marriage licenses|date=2013-09-04|accessdate=2013-09-04|archive-date=2019-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190527004847/https://www.kob.com/article/stories/S3148764.shtml?cat=500|dead-url=no}}</ref>同时，[[聖米格爾縣_(新墨西哥州)|聖米格爾縣]]和[[巴倫西亞縣|巴倫西亞縣]]的工作人员也开始允许同性婚姻登记。<ref name="koat">{{cite news|url=http://www.koat.com/news/new-mexico/albuquerque/2-more-nm-counties-to-issue-gay-marriage-licenses/-/9153728/21668044/-/2k4q0k/-/index.html|title=2 more NM counties to issue gay marriage licenses|date=2013-08-27|publisher=KOAT|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022125741/http://www.koat.com/news/new-mexico/albuquerque/2-more-nm-counties-to-issue-gay-marriage-licenses/-/9153728/21668044/-/2k4q0k/-/index.html|archivedate=2013年10月22日}}</ref>

2013年8月29日，新墨西哥州各县投票一致要求州最高法院对同性婚姻的合法性作出裁决。10月23日最高法院举行了听证会。2013年12月19日，该法院一致决定同性婚姻合法，使得新墨西哥州成为美国第17个同性婚姻合法的州。

